    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "cilium_drop by reason (전체)",
      "description": "노드 데이터패스 drop 사유 전체. **'Packet too big'/'Fragmentation needed'=MTU/DSR**, 'No mapping for NAT'/'backend'=LB/SNAT, 'CT: Map insertion failed'=맵포화. (node 단위라 namespace 귀속은 아래 Hubble)\\n임계선:1/10.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 7
      },
      "maxDataPoints": 600,
      "interval": "30s",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource}"
          },
          "expr": "sum by(reason)(rate(cilium_drop_count_total{cluster=\"$cluster\",project=\"$project\",node=~\"$nodename\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{reason}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "pps",
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
